Package com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor.mkv

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EbmlReader
    Event-driven EBML reader that delivers events to an EbmlReaderOutput.
    EbmlReaderOutput
    Defines EBML element IDs/types and reacts to events.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultEbmlReader
    Default implementation of EbmlReader.
    DefaultEbmlReader.MasterElement
    Used in DefaultEbmlReader.masterElementsStack to track when the current master element ends, so that EbmlReaderOutput.endMasterElement(int) can be called.
    DefaultEbmlReaderTest
    Tests DefaultEbmlReader.
    DefaultEbmlReaderTest.TestOutput
    An EbmlReaderOutput that records each event callback.
    MatroskaExtractor
    Extracts data from the Matroska and WebM container formats.
    MatroskaExtractor.Track  
    MatroskaExtractorTest
    Tests for MatroskaExtractor.
    Sniffer
    Utility class that peeks from the input stream in order to determine whether it appears to be compatible input for this extractor.
    VarintReader
    Reads EBML variable-length integers (varints) from an ExtractorInput.
    VarintReaderTest
    Tests for VarintReader.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    MatroskaExtractor.Flags
    Flags controlling the behavior of the extractor.
